91
00:03:40,769 --> 00:03:42,290
as a part of China…

92
00:03:42,290 --> 00:03:45,919
Let’s just hope they don’t nuke the wrong
country...

93
00:03:45,919 --> 00:03:48,309
slash region.

94
00:03:48,309 --> 00:03:52,590
And Mercedes-Benz has also just made a huge
mistake.

95
