101
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,620
Just kidding.

102
00:04:06,620 --> 00:04:07,520
Again.

103
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,500
They called Mercedes an enemy

104
00:04:09,510 --> 00:04:12,139
