108
00:04:17,850 --> 00:04:20,340
They also replaced the ad with this new one.

109
00:04:20,340 --> 00:04:21,890
What’s that, Shelley?

110
00:04:21,890 --> 00:04:24,540
That’s not a real Mao quote?!

111
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:25,540
I guess Mercedes-Benz

112
00:04:25,540 --> 00:04:26,540
is going to have to issue

113
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,730
a third apology.

114
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:29,730
In other news,

115
00:04:29,730 --> 00:04:31,560
Sweden has been having bad luck

116
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,750
when it comes to keeping its citizens

117
00:04:33,750 --> 00:04:37,120
from being abducted by Chinese authorities.

118
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:39,930
So the Swedish government has taken a novel
approach

119
00:04:39,930 --> 00:04:42,710
