128
00:05:02,630 --> 00:05:04,900
and demand Gui Minhai be released.

129
00:05:04,900 --> 00:05:08,090
Gui Minhai was “picked up by plainclothes
agents

130
00:05:08,090 --> 00:05:11,440
on January 20th as he travelled on a train
to Beijing

131
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:13,370
with two Swedish diplomats.”

132
