I feel like the diplomats should have intervened.

133
00:05:17,590 --> 00:05:18,840
But I guess that wouldn’t have been

134
00:05:18,840 --> 00:05:20,670
very diplomatic, would it?

135
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:23,080
Gui Minhai was one of the Hong Kong booksellers

136
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:25,790
who had in the past been detained for publishing

137
00:05:25,790 --> 00:05:29,410
controversial books about Chinese leader Xi
Jinping.

138
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:31,230
He spent two years in detention,

139
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:32,520
even though—again—

140
00:05:32,520 --> 00:05:34,020
