152
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:56,800
So the Party is pushing

153
00:05:56,800 --> 00:06:01,020
“300 million people into winter sports by
[2022]

154
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:03,120
with at least 800 ski resorts,

155
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:05,640
